The paper discusses bibliometric parameters and the evaluation of research units, which are related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The study also focuses on productivity and impact metrics, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) and security and privacy (cs.CR). Finally, the study is specific to the field of science and technology, which could relate to social and information networks (cs.SI).
